-Mildweasel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulanlaornplaneswalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LanlaornPlaneswalker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/29/01 10:32 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Antigate=Suicide</span><hr size=1> The spell does not work like a lure, in fact on the lvl 51 one's resist line it reads:<br>
